# Migration data dumps must never be committed — historical PII / hashed
# admin credentials / pre-launch tester rows. The existing
# packages/db/prisma/_migration-data.json file in git history is being
# scrubbed (P0-1); this rule prevents accidental re-add.
packages/db/prisma/_migration-data.json
packages/db/prisma/_migration-data*.json

